* On Thursday, we will have an optional dinner at [Homeslice](https://www.happycamper.pizza/homeslice/) to help build community. You will be able to purchase your own food/drink and we will have a reserved seating area in their heated, outdoor patio.
* On other nights, you will be responsible for dinners; there are many restaurants within easy walking distance of both DePaul (see [Dining options near DePaul University, Lincoln Park](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1T4lULBxdB1bgJNQgfkwVe0S09zk0BVBrrOJEDMpPK6M/edit?usp=sharing)) and the hotel. We will provide opportunities for you to coordinate with each other around meals.

